FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How can I access the data?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: You can access our data through our intuitive web interface or via our API. Our platform offers powerful querying and filtering capabilities to help you find the specific information you need.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, our data is updated in real-time as new blocks are added to the respective blockchain networks. You can be confident that you're working with the latest information.

PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Blockchain Explorer App
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: A blockchain explorer is a tool that allows you to view and search data on a blockchain network. It provides a user-friendly interface to explore transaction details, wallet addresses, and other blockchain information.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app connects to various blockchain nodes and parses the data to provide a comprehensive view of the network activity. You can search for specific transactions, addresses, or blocks using our powerful search functionality.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Currently, we support popular blockchains like Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin, and more. We are constantly working to add support for new blockchain networks based on user demand.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is your app free to use?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our blockchain explorer app is completely free to use. We believe in providing open access to blockchain data for everyone.
